{"tid":576643,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"DSE嘅認受性","createTime":"2018-03-01T05:21:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T11:59:18.000Z","uid":65844,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9ababee20a927ca344c5854033a208c4cde33fc8","tid":576643,"uid":65844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:21:30.000Z","msg":"考評局已完成基準研究，比較2012年文憑試英國語文科的成績與國際英語水平測試(IELTS) 的水平。下表列出文憑試英國語文科第2至5**級對應的IELTS分數。這項研究是以分層抽樣方式，邀請2012年文憑試考生參與，然後就考生的文憑試等級與 IELTS分數作出比較。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n文憑試英國語文科等級<br />\n對應IELTS整體分數<br />\n5**\t=7.51 &ndash; 7.77<br />\n5*\t=7.16 &ndash; 7.32<br />\n5=\t6.81 &ndash; 6.99<br />\n4=\t6.31 &ndash; 6.51<br />\n3\t=5.48 &ndash; 5.68<br />\n2\t=4.79 &ndash; 5.07<br />\n<br />\n公務員事務局係承認DSE嘅, 好多大公司亦都有睇DSE成績<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提IELTS 報名費係 HKD2040"},{"pid":"10221c19ab63d8c8fae3bc1942fdce926bfb6f6e","tid":576643,"uid":136618,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:53:04.000Z","msg":"都係收皮罷啦<br />\n<br />\n我朋友DSE3，IELTS 7.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd40e515b5db47a084ad4a6b1ab9b7f01fa9a02","tid":576643,"uid":815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"10221c19ab63d8c8fae3bc1942fdce926bfb6f6e","tid":576643,"uid":136618,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:53:04.000Z","msg":"都係收皮罷啦<br />\n<br />\n我朋友DSE3，IELTS 7.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T09:58:37.000Z","msg":"無人識你朋友呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acdfbfc8fec09cf3d420103abebff466cd3c21a5","tid":576643,"uid":137233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfd40e515b5db47a084ad4a6b1ab9b7f01fa9a02","tid":576643,"uid":815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"10221c19ab63d8c8fae3bc1942fdce926bfb6f6e","tid":576643,